      <p class="mt-xxlg">
      Hotnight is an app project that my friend and I started  to help travelers in Whistler, BC find hostel rooms during the skii season. Hotnight lets you set email notifications to watch when a spot becomes available at your favourite hostel. So far we've integrated five different locations and are working on adding many more in BC and Alberta.</p>

      <p>Since James Mastuba and I created this app in the early spring of 2016, weâ€™ve grown to a team of 4 and acquired 150 users, many of which use Hotnight regularly in Whistler. We love to work on Hotnight as a side project and are constantly working on improving its features and user experience.</p>

      <p>We've improved the user experience since the initial design, but we are working on creating a new, more clean and simple user experience and interface for hotnight.ca. We are also adjusting the experience according to user feedback and error reports.</p>

